Body: Blockchain-Based Lottery System, MOS Lottery, Introduces New Way to Bet On Closing Stock Prices  https://s14.postimg.org/gru39lbtt/stockmarketlottery.jpg    Geneva, Switzerland (STL.News) MOS Lottery, a blockchain-based lottery system created to address the problems inherited in the lottery market today, this week officially launched its comprehensive platform, providing a new kind of way to bet on closing stock prices.  Through the Ethereum blockchain based smart contract, all bets and results are made public in the system, recorded on the shared ledger without any third party involvement or interference. Uniquely, the lottery winning number is selected from the global stock market index, like NASDAQ or the Dow Jones.  â€œAlthough governments and states, for years, have been operating their own lottery systems, there has been fraudulent activity and transparency questions,â€ said Alexander Mittler, CEO of MOS Lottery. â€œSince we have witnessed, time and time again, a centralized system failing participants, weâ€™ve introduced a decentralized approach based entirely upon an Ethereum smart contracts. Even more special, our numbers are selected from public platform, preventing manipulation.â€  The Ethereum smart contract also ensures there are sufficient pools of fund to pay the winning amount before any bet is accepted, assuring players they receive their correct payouts should they win the lottery.  â€œAt this point in time, there is no other system that is comparable to what we are doing here at MOS Lottery,â€ said Mittler. â€œTherefore, we are proud to launch an Initial Coin Offering to grow our jackpot fund and accelerate our official market debut. Itâ€™s our goal to raise 55 million USD. Help us get there.â€  Over 5.5 billion MOS Tokens, the platformâ€™s decentralized currency, will be available to investors. Once the ICO is funded, the platform will officially go live.  For more information, visit: www.moscoin.io  About MOS Lottery MOS Lottery is a decentralized, blockchain-based lottery system that picks winning numbers from the closing statistics at NASDAQ, the Dow Jones, and so forth. As opposed to the centralized lottery systems regulated by the government, MOS Lottery, built atop Ethereum smart contracts, essentially removes all elements of fraudulent activity and interference.  Before taking the concept to market, MOS Lottery will host an Initial Coin Offering, with 5.5 billion MOS Tokens available to interested investors.

Body: An Overview of MOS Incentive Programs  https://s14.postimg.org/u2dcp5uy9/Screen_Shot_2018-03-15_at_11.15.37.png  The best product, game, or service ever invented will not achieve profitability if no one knows about it.  That is why, like many other businesses and lottery programs before us, MOS has created a unique incentive program for those who love the idea of a completely transparent blockchain lottery.  Our goal is simple: to build our community by encouraging people like you to refer potential investors. When an investor purchases MOS tokens, then we reward you with free MOS tokens.  Our bounty pool for our incentive program is limited to 500 million MOS tokens. Once the limit has been reached, then unfortunately we cannot pay a reward for future referrals afterward.  We have also set the maximum eligible reward at 1 million MOS tokens to ensure everyone who is passionate about our platform can get involved.  What Rewards Can I Earn from the MOS Incentive Program?  We offer three tiers of rewards for those who refer investors to join our community. There are minimum MOS token purchases required for a free reward bonus to be issued.  Â· A referred investor purchase of 10,000 MOS tokens minimum offers a bonus of 500 MOS tokens to the referrer.  Â· A referred investor who purchases 100,000 MOS tokens minimum will create a bonus of 5,000 MOS tokens to the referrer.  Â· A referred investment of 1 million MOS tokens generates a bonus of 50,000 MOS tokens to the referrer.  For referrers to qualify for this bounty program, you must sign up, then login, to the MOS ITS. Your dashboard will then display your personalized referral link. You are welcome to share it throughout your digital network: social media, email, chat, and more.  If someone clicks on the shared link, they will be directed to our main landing page. Their link will be tracked to your account. Any bonus tokens earned are immediately and automatically credited to your wallet once the referred investor completes their purchase.  Why Encourage an Investment into MOS Tokens?  MOS tokens are more than a gateway to a fun stock market lottery. They are also a chance to earn profit. All MOS token investors are entitled to their proportional share of 15% of the monthly gross profit from the lottery.  All sales and payouts are recorded on the Ethereum blockchain, making them a public record. The smart contract will automatically determine the gross profit and credit rewards to token holders automatically.  MOS tokens must be parked in our wallet to be eligible for this distribution.  By creating this rewarding format, we envision a strong demand for MOS tokens in the future as more investors realize the full potential of this platform.  Investors benefit in two ways: with increased pricing of the MOS tokens and their monthly proportional share of platform gross profits.  We are creating a platform with a fixed supply and an anticipated increase in demand. Our early investors may see the biggest rewards, but there is still time to get involved. As long as there are still referral bonuses available, there will be opportunities to grow your investment and have fun.  Thatâ€™s why MOS has one of the most exciting incentive programs in our industry today.  www.moscoin.io

Author: TSM.Global
Title: [ANN] ðŸ“ˆ MOS ðŸš€ - World's 1st Decentralized Stock Market Lottery Platform ðŸŒŽ
Body: How MOS Created a Different Blockchain Lottery Program  https://s14.postimg.org/hbvudsev5/believe.png  A simple search on your preferred search engine will provide you with numerous blockchain lottery listings.  Kibo Partners, Fire Lotto, SmartBillions, and others are all joining MOS in pioneering a new gaming experience for people utilizing the world of crypto. Each takes its own unique approach to the gaming experience, but there are some processes that they have in common.  Â· Many of the blockchain lotteries are structured to provide winning numbers based on future block hashes or random number generators.  Â· We all utilize a smart contract-based platform that is based off Ethereum, then utilize tickets or tokens to represent gaming opportunities.  Â· Multiple game options are offered to entice casual internet users, crypto experts, and an anonymous, but global community of players.  Our investing structures are also quite similar.  Blockchain lotteries offer a pre-sale where tickets or tokens are sold at prices that are fixed and low. This begins the prize pool generation process. Over time, the goal is to have the price of those tickets or tokens to increase because they can be traded as a commodity, just like any other cryptocurrency.  Every single blockchain states that they have the most transparent system in place. Yet, at MOS, we feel like no one takes transparency more seriously than us. That is how we are different.  Why Transparency Matters for a Blockchain Lottery  We believe transparency matters because players deserve to have clear, honest information about how their gaming numbers are generated.  At Fire Lotto, a random number generator is used. Players are permitted to inspect the code used for the generator at their convenience.  SmartBillions uses the hashes of the third future block to generate their bet results.  Kibo Partners simply says that the gambling rules and conditions are â€œhard-wired into the architectureâ€ of their open-source smart contracts.  At MOS, we searched for a better way to encourage transparency, while still keeping the lottery aspect to the gaming process. Thatâ€™s how we developed the idea of the â€œstock market lottery.â€  Our bet results are based on the closing indices of the stock markets. The closing indices are sent to the blockchains via APIs with results that are easy to verify.  Check any news site or the index itself to verify that the numbers issued are correct.  Hereâ€™s an example. Letâ€™s say that the Dow Jones Industrial Average closes at 24,852.39. Now letâ€™s say that the NASDAQ Composite closes at 6,838.72. You would instantly know the results, based on the game you played.  1-Digit Game: 9  2-Digit Game: 39  4-Digit Game: 3972, etc  Once the supplying index value is appropriately communicated, like any other blockchain lottery, instant payouts occur to the playerâ€™s wallet.  At MOS, we want you to have access to a lottery game that is truly transparent and fun to play. This structure allows us to appeal to anyone from any background because it is easy to understand.  Our platform is secure. Game play is anonymous. Our bet results are the only option that can be independently verified in just seconds by anyone.  That is how MOS has created a different, and we would say better, blockchain lottery platform for you to enjoy.  www.moscoin.io

Title: [ANN] ðŸ“ˆ MOS ðŸš€ - World's 1st Decentralized Stock Market Lottery Platform ðŸŒŽ
Body: How MOS Creates a Fair Playing Field   https://s14.postimg.org/v3dle5twh/jackpot.jpg   A lottery must create a fair playing field for all parties involved. That means the playing format must be transparent and easy to understand for players. It also means the House Edge must be able to provide an assured profit over time to ensure that platform operations can continue.  That is why we have taken specific steps to ensure that the stock market lottery from MOS is able to achieve both goals without interfering from the fun and competitiveness that we hope our community is able to enjoy.  How We Create a House Edge That Is Fair  As much as weâ€™d like to give away everything to our players, there are certain operating expenses that must be covered to keep the lottery platform active.  At MOS, we believe that balancing the need for profits with a need to provide rewards for investors is extremely important.  For that reason, the MOS house edge is set at 10% within the smart contract. No one can change this value, not even us. Then, out of that 10%, we allocate 6% toward the jackpot pool. We use 2% to reward affiliates, based on their performance, and the other 2% is reserved to facilitate ongoing operations.  How We Create a Fair Playing Field  When we took a look at our competition, we realized that we had a different idea of transparency. Instead of random number generators or hashes on future blocks, we felt like there was a better way.  Thatâ€™s when we thought about the worldâ€™s major stock markets. By utilizing a global system of stock market indices, we can still allow players to participate throughout the day, while still offering complete transparency of the best results.  We developed a 5-step process that ensures the playing field remains fair for everyone.  #1. Players select the game mode which suits them best. Then they purchase the corresponding lottery ticket for that game by using MOS tokens.  #2. The smart contract checks the jackpot pool, making sure a sufficient payout is possible. A bet will not be accepted if the payout is not sufficient. Bets are not accepted if the stock market exchange being utilized is closed either.  #3. Thirty minutes before the closing of the stock market, player transactions are posted to the Ethereum blockchain.  #4. Upon stock market closure, MOS retrieves the indices via APIs.  #5. Then we use the final two digits in the stock market indices to create the winning numbers, using a pattern that cannot be change.  By using different stock market indices in varying time zones, we are able to create all-day play with more transparency. Information comes from London, the United States, Germany, Shanghai, and more.  This format allows us to create a fun playing format for everyone.  Lotteries are fun to play because they have simple rules and the hope of a big payout. Our unique structure allows these advantages to be combined with the world of crypto to create a modern lottery experience.  For more about how MOS works, please take a few moments to read our full whitepaper.  www.moscoin.io
